{"tid":1388706,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新戰線：修改公安條例，廢除暴動罪","createTime":"2019-07-30T18:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:18:53.000Z","uid":269766,"like":127,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a2655793f7e816c6093df93e2a924636257b1cb4","tid":1388706,"uid":269766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:07:30.000Z","msg":"上環一役44位義士被控暴動罪，我想信好多人都好似我咁怒火中燒。喺呢一刻，一班義士係葵涌淋雨、中椒、俾白皮肥狗攞住支槍指嚇。希望後方既文宣/論述巴打都可以幫幫手，為前線提供更加多思想彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我認為，而家係適當時候，亦有足夠民意基礎，開闢一條新（輿論）戰線：＂修改公安條例、完全廢除暴動罪＂！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n簡單回帶：2016年魚蛋革命，幾十人被控暴動罪。但因為當時社會普遍唔同情梁天琦／其他烈士，所以好少人喊＂撤銷暴動罪＂，更遑論要求修改《公安條例》。<br />\n<br />\n但由2019年3月開始蘊讓既反送中，經歷6.12開槍，7.1佔領立會，大家都要求釋放義士、撤回暴動定性。義士既犧牲得到大家認同，連中產、學者、泛民和理非KOL都唔割蓆。<span style=\"color: red;\">我地有理由相信，今晚警犬正式起訴暴動罪，會造成更大輿論反撲，令新一輪抗爭變得更聚焦</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>所以，我地要做既，係回歸我地反送中既＂初心＂，直接指出《公安條例》下暴動罪惡法既不義<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>戰線一：警黑暴行</strong><br />\n<em>目的：重奪＂暴動＂既定義</em><br />\n戰線一最簡單，其實大家已經做緊。直接羅列撐警廢老／白衣人／黑警既暴行，指出佢地既行為模式係一班人（集結）持武、主動出擊、並且以製造恐慌為樂（破壞社會安寧）。所以，呢班人先係參與暴動。<span style=\"color: red;\">We don't burn, you burn.</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>戰線二：國際慣例</strong><br />\n<em>目的：引經據典，爭取和理非同情</em><br />\n和理非最中意參考國際慣例，而事實上政府既政策亦需要參考外國例子。我地有必要指出香港既<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">暴動罪無論喺定義、立法原意、同罰則上都係過時</span></strong>、只應該屬於第三世界既產物。<span style=\"color: green;\">英國喺1973年已經全面廢除暴動罪</span>。而暴動罪喺加拿大、芬蘭、冰島、同美國哥倫比亞既最高判刑都唔會超過4年。<span style=\"color: blue;\">喺加拿大，執法者更加需要先作出呼籲，容許示威者係30分鐘之內離開，然後先至可以用暴動罪拉人。</span><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/y4ch7b9t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy4ch7b9t&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kUv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=49e70105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/y4ch7b9t</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>戰線三：回顧歷史</strong><br />\n<em>目的：令建至陷於被動</em><br />\n香港既暴動罪係當時殖民政府為左對付六七暴動而訂立既法例。諷刺既係港英根本冇用過暴動罪起訴左仔。為左回顧共黨既光輝歷史，我地好應該翻查史料，展示六七左仔既行徑，等大家重溫下咩野先係真正意義既暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>後續戰線：向專業人士（e.g. 大律師公會）施壓，形成新一輪社會共識，要求商界表態、法改委（Law Reform Commission）重新檢討／廢除暴動罪</strong></span>"},{"pid":"00b67c8a4783d7be33e6b31412bae12f85a59630","tid":1388706,"uid":64380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f634b0311cc5289d72f1c2a1f5d75680ea021974","tid":1388706,"uid":269766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:09:32.000Z","msg":"打得太快，有錯字請海涵，push"},{"pid":"a4e6d9e70373397ffa598b048a64a401bf1731f3","tid":1388706,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後日(8月1)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kUv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=9198f6e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kUv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=083c0ffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地係今日係旺角東天橋擺街站的手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1387289/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1387289/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"76142f1304c26f88822e643ad39a8cf21a6b5d71","tid":1388706,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:11:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a34d3f7780f840a03c8585524a5dd264e010a243","tid":1388706,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"0d0884eb8f91070bd2e79fbde717b75666b13837","tid":1388706,"uid":200801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:12:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08550ac04cc12737bc6f9e2eede4e0485470c899","tid":1388706,"uid":269766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dbe3d7fa9bade95f6231711ab55e156a108f915d","tid":1388706,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:15:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d3915db26648e5b7490e27fc543b0e22a14b041b","tid":1388706,"uid":12086,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"係廢除公安條款 <br />\n97前係已經廢除但臨立會再立返法"},{"pid":"101ca51cac9435eb9f9649fad85c6914de00c634","tid":1388706,"uid":260236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"8月5日齊罷工"},{"pid":"278e9f9b8f4ab10367557a381e191e1d6e2b85f1","tid":1388706,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:44:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7d1573c333d76a9fcf